---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import FactoryAnimation from '../components/FactoryAnimation.astro';
import CountUp from '../components/CountUp.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Navvi Corporations | Factory Transformation, SewCoach and SewTrak"
  description="Navvi helps garment manufacturers cut waste, build systems and boost profits with factory transformation, SewCoach training and SewTrak production tracking."
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero visual-band">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-entrance">
          <p class="eyebrow">Garment factory transformation</p>
          <h1>Cut waste. Build systems. Boost profits.</h1>
          <p class="lead">Navvi helps garment manufacturers save ₹3-10 Cr annually, train line-ready operators, and track production live through SewCoach and SewTrak.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://wa.me/919894466715?text=Hello%20Navvi%2C%20I%20want%20a%20free%20factory%20assessment.">WhatsApp Free Assessment</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/sewtrak/">See SewTrak</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-panel">
          <div class="metric-grid" data-reveal-group>
            <div class="metric" data-reveal>
              <CountUp value="8.5" prefix="₹" suffix=" Cr" />
              <span>Average annual savings in flagship transformation work</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric" data-reveal>
              <CountUp value="90" suffix=" days" decimals={0} />
              <span>Initial turnaround timeline for measurable factory improvement</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric" data-reveal>
              <CountUp value="1800" suffix="+" decimals={0} />
              <span>Operators trained through SewCoach-style capability programs</span>
            </div>
            <div class="metric" data-reveal>
              <strong>Live</strong>
              <span>Production, HRIS, OTIF and KPI visibility through SewTrak</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <FactoryAnimation />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">Three connected offers</p>
          <h2>One ecosystem for factory owners.</h2>
          <p class="muted">Use Navvi for full transformation, SewCoach for operator training systems, and SewTrak for planning, tracking and production control.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3" data-reveal-group>
          <article class="card card-featured" data-reveal>
            <span class="kicker">Transformation</span>
            <h3>Factory profit system</h3>
            <p class="muted">Free assessment, 90-day sprint, interim staff support, KPI dashboards, SOPs and execution on the shop floor.</p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Reduce rework, delay and process loss.</li>
              <li>Improve RFT, OWE, OTIF and cash cycle.</li>
              <li>Build daily control with dashboards.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline" href="/factory-transformation/">Explore transformation</a></p>
          </article>
          <article class="card" data-reveal>
            <span class="kicker">Training</span>
            <h3>SewCoach</h3>
            <p class="muted">Set up a scientific sewing operator training room with certified trainers, LMS courses, OJT tracking and certification.</p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Make new operators line-ready in 8 days.</li>
              <li>Run ToT and GPOT programs.</li>
              <li>Use the app for progress and cycle timing.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline" href="/sewcoach/">Explore SewCoach</a></p>
          </article>
          <article class="card" data-reveal>
            <span class="kicker">Tracking</span>
            <h3>SewTrak</h3>
            <p class="muted">A garment resource planner and production tracker for live planning, production entry, KPIs, HRIS and OTIF control.</p>
            <ul class="list">
              <li>Plan orders, routes, SAM and manpower.</li>
              <li>Track output, WIP and line efficiency.</li>
              <li>Control roles, reports and dashboards.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a class="btn btn-outline" href="/sewtrak/">Explore SewTrak</a></p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-blue visual-band">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">What we fix</p>
          <h2>The silent profit leaks inside garment factories.</h2>
          <p class="muted">Most factories do not lose money in one place. Loss hides in many small daily gaps.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3" data-reveal-group>
          <div class="card card-blue" data-reveal><h3>Low RFT</h3><p>Rework, late delivery, buyer pressure and hidden cost.</p></div>
          <div class="card card-blue" data-reveal><h3>Weak OWE</h3><p>Paid minutes leak through poor line balance and poor flow.</p></div>
          <div class="card card-blue" data-reveal><h3>Slow cash cycle</h3><p>Inventory days, fabric delay and order closing gaps trap working capital.</p></div>
          <div class="card card-blue" data-reveal><h3>Training delay</h3><p>New operators take too long to reach production-ready efficiency.</p></div>
          <div class="card card-blue" data-reveal><h3>No live tracking</h3><p>Leaders see issues late because production data stays on paper or Excel.</p></div>
          <div class="card card-blue" data-reveal><h3>HR gaps</h3><p>Absenteeism, attrition and skill mismatch reduce daily output.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="proof-bar" data-reveal-group>
          <div class="proof-item" data-reveal>
            <strong>₹3-10 Cr</strong>
            <span>Annual saving potential we target for eligible factories</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-item" data-reveal>
            <strong>10-15 Cr</strong>
            <span>Working capital unlock opportunity in large operations</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-item" data-reveal>
            <CountUp value="40" suffix="%+" decimals={0} />
            <span>SewCoach operator efficiency target by Day 8</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-item" data-reveal>
            <CountUp value="5" suffix=" slots" decimals={0} />
            <span>Monthly free assessment capacity for serious factories</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container split">
        <div data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">The Navvi way</p>
          <h2>Assess. Prove. Scale. Sustain.</h2>
          <p class="muted">We do not stop with reports. We install operating systems, train people and track the numbers until the factory can run the rhythm internally.</p>
          <div class="section-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/case-results/">View anonymous results</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/contact/">Talk to Navvi</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-2 steps steps-timeline" data-steps-timeline data-reveal-group>
          <div class="card step" data-reveal><h3>Assess</h3><p class="muted">Walk the floor, collect baseline KPIs and map loss.</p></div>
          <div class="card step" data-reveal><h3>Prove</h3><p class="muted">Run quick wins with supervisors, operators and dashboards.</p></div>
          <div class="card step" data-reveal><h3>Scale</h3><p class="muted">Move from one line or department to full production rhythm.</p></div>
          <div class="card step" data-reveal><h3>Sustain</h3><p class="muted">Train internal owners and review data through daily control.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section section-blue visual-band">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">Where to start</p>
          <h2>Choose the right first move.</h2>
          <p class="muted">You do not need to buy everything at once. Start where the leak is clearest.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-3" data-reveal-group>
          <article class="card" data-reveal>
            <span class="kicker">Profit leak</span>
            <h3>Start with Factory Assessment</h3>
            <p class="muted">Choose this if rework, delay, low efficiency, fabric loss or cash cycle is hurting profit.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/factory-transformation/">See assessment</a>
          </article>
          <article class="card" data-reveal>
            <span class="kicker">People leak</span>
            <h3>Start with SewCoach</h3>
            <p class="muted">Choose this if new operators take too long to become line-ready or training depends on one trainer.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/sewcoach/">See SewCoach</a>
          </article>
          <article class="card" data-reveal>
            <span class="kicker">Data leak</span>
            <h3>Start with SewTrak</h3>
            <p class="muted">Choose this if production, HR, WIP, OTIF and line performance are not visible during the day.</p>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/sewtrak/">See SewTrak</a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container split">
        <div data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">Product proof</p>
          <h2>Real apps. Real dashboards. Real floor use.</h2>
          <p class="muted">Product screenshots, training assets and animated KPI graphics help buyers see Navvi as an execution ecosystem, not a brochure.</p>
          <div class="section-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/sewtrak/">View SewTrak screens</a>
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/sewcoach/">View SewCoach</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-preview" data-reveal-group>
          <a class="product-preview-main media-frame" href="/sewtrak/#screens" data-parallax data-reveal>
            <img src="/assets/sewtrak/dashboard.png" alt="SewTrak dashboard showing production flow" loading="lazy" />
            <span class="product-preview-label">SewTrak dashboard</span>
          </a>
          <div class="product-preview-grid">
            <a class="product-preview-item media-frame" href="/sewtrak/#screens" data-parallax data-reveal>
              <img src="/assets/sewtrak/kpis.png" alt="SewTrak KPI dashboard" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="product-preview-label">KPI screen</span>
            </a>
            <a class="product-preview-item media-frame" href="/sewcoach/" data-parallax data-reveal>
              <img src="/assets/sewcoach/sewcoach-flyer.png" alt="SewCoach training system flyer" loading="lazy" />
              <span class="product-preview-label">SewCoach programs</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container grid-2">
        <div data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">Common questions</p>
          <h2>Simple answers before you call.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq" data-reveal-group>
          <details open data-reveal>
            <summary>Do you show pricing on the website?</summary>
            <p class="muted">No. Factory size, problem depth and support needed decide the engagement. We discuss scope after the first assessment or demo.</p>
          </details>
          <details data-reveal>
            <summary>Can client names be shared?</summary>
            <p class="muted">Not publicly. Many factories prefer confidentiality. We use anonymous case results online and discuss context in person where permitted.</p>
          </details>
          <details data-reveal>
            <summary>Can we start only with SewCoach or SewTrak?</summary>
            <p class="muted">Yes. You can start with training, tracking or full transformation depending on the current business pain.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-tight">
      <div class="container cta-panel" data-reveal>
        <div>
          <h2>Ready to find the leaks?</h2>
          <p>Book a free factory assessment. We will confirm by WhatsApp and schedule the first discussion.</p>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://wa.me/919894466715?text=Hello%20Navvi%2C%20I%20want%20to%20book%20a%20free%20factory%20assessment.">Book on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>